"{\"uid\": \"wnd.com-2024-06-watch-former-iowa-coach-speaks-caitlin-clark-not-picked-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByAround the Web  June 11, 2024  (WASHINGTON POST) - MS. JENKINS: Hello, and welcome to Washington Post Live.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 49, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Washington_Post\", \"score\": 0.9999999783985916, \"rank\": 2.160135318640656e-08, \"text\": \"WASHINGTON POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Washington_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Washington_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 88, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Wizards\", \"score\": 0.8156730400141352, \"rank\": 0.1925366795714075, \"text\": \"Washington\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Wizards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Wizards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am Sally Jenkins.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 115, \"end\": 128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sally_Jenkins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sally Jenkins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sally_Jenkins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sally_Jenkins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a sports columnist for The Post, and we are here today for the latest in our series, \\\"Leveling the Playing Field.\\\"\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And our guest is former Iowa Hawkeyes women's basketball coach Lisa Bluder.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.9525426041242031, \"rank\": 0.04578091535112718, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Bluder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lisa Bluder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Bluder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Bluder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lisa, welcome to the show.\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are so glad to have you today.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MS. BLUDER: Oh, it's my pleasure, and I am still not used to hearing that word \\\"former\\\" before my title and my name there.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It still feels weird.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@LisaBluderon Caitlin Clark being left off the women's Olympic team, \\\"I obviously would have loved to have seen her on that team \\u2026 But we have to remember it the hardest team to make.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 12 women they have chosen are exceptional women.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My only but is, what about the future?\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"pic.twitter.com/937CET0WeK  - Washington Post Live (@PostLive)June 10, 2024    MS. JENKINS: Hey, it feels weird for the rest of us.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was sick-I was sick at heart when I heard you were hanging up your spurs, because you are obviously one of the greats of the-in the entire history of the game, and we are going to get to your record.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read the full story \\u203a  You must belogged into post a comment.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"About us  Subscribe  Go Ad-Free  Privacy policy  Copyright \\u00a9 2026 WorldNetDaily  Copyright \\u00a9 2026 WorldNetDaily  March 22, 2026  Joe Kovacs  March 22, 2026  Joe Kovacs  March 22, 2026  RealClearWire\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.7974111826237018, \"rank\": 0.23631926992245206, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.7974111826237018, \"rank\": 0.23631926992245206, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}]}]}"